
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-wei-abfab-fcla-02.txt'>
    <title>"Federated Cross-Layer Access", Yinxing Wei</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-wei-abfab-fcla-02.txt</link>
    <description>Network stratum and application stratum form a federation to faciliate user's access.  Network operator acts as Identity Provider (IdP), and application reuses underlying network's security capabilities to simlify application's access.  This document is to introduce such federated cross-layer access use case and message flows.</description>
    <dc:date>2012-03-11T23:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
